modDescription:
This is a mod you can use right out of the gate although it requires a tad extra wood. It’s called the Steelwood Mod because it’s an extremely durable alternative option to the default [storage](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-storage/).

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IKUtn-C2OMrH_sffBXNJkS0KQ5pzj9FW/view?usp=sharing)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/21494-alucards-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Noisy Pants](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/noisy-pants/)
